com.thomsonreuters.upa.examples.niprovider

Class MarketPriceHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thomsonreuters.upa.examples.niprovider.MarketPriceHandler

  • public class MarketPriceHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the market price handler for the UPA NIProvider application. It provides methods to encode and send refreshes and updates, as well as close streams.
